Technical diagram: AI Agent Architecture - core components in a container. Center: LLM (brain icon). Four surrounding modules connected: 1) Memory (History + Vector Store), 2) Tool Registry (search, calc, db_query icons), 3) Planner (strategy icon), 4) Executor (gear icon), 5) Safety Guard (shield icon). Outer ring: Human-in-the-Loop checkpoint. Clean technical architecture style, German labels, dark theme.